SUMMARY:
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
 We are proposing to amend the Mexican fruit fly regulations by adding a high-temperature forced air treatment for
grapefruit. This proposed action would provide an alternative treatment for grapefruit that require treatment
to be moved interstate from regulated areas in Texas and California. Adding this treatment would facilitate the interstate
movement of grapefruit grown in regulated areas.
