<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(c) Require prime contractors whose contracts include the following clauses to include those clauses, without modification
except for appropriate identification of the parties, in contracts with subcontractors or suppliers, at all tiers,
who will be furnishing technical data in response to a government requirement. 
