Scope of subpart.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
This subpart_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(a) Prescribes policies and procedures for the acquisition of computer software and computer software documentation,
and the rights to use, modify, reproduce, release, perform, display, or disclosure such software or documentation.
It implements requirements in the following laws and Executive Order:
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 02 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=15 g=1 f=1 -->
10 U.S.C. 2302(4)
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
10 U.S.C. 2305 (subsection (d)(4))
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
10 U.S.C. 2320
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
10 U.S.C. 2321
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
10 U.S.C. 2325
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Executive Order 12591 (subsection 1(b)(6))
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 02 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(b) Does not apply to computer software or computer software documentation acquired under GSA schedule contracts.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

