into a deliverable software item unless the contractor has obtained an appropriate license for the Government and,
when applicable, others acting on the Government's behalf, or has obtained the contracting officer's written approval
to do so. Grant approval to use third party copyrighted software in which the Government will not receive a copyright
license only when the Government's requirements cannot be satisfied without the third party material or when the
