processes, flow charts, formulae and related material that would enable the software to be reproduced, recreated,
or recompiled. Computer software does not include computer data bases or computer software documentation. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(4) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=3 -->
Computer software documentation
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

