items, regardless of storage medium, that explain the capabilities of the computer software or provide instructions
for using the software. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(5) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=3 -->
Detailed manufacturing or process data
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=1 -->
 means technical data that describe the steps, sequences, and conditions of manufacturing, processing or assembly
used by the manufacturer to produce an item or component or to perform a process. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(6) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=3 -->
Developed
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=1 -->
