to a government contract, and partially with costs charged directly to a government contract. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(10) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=3 -->
